    "Ablation Study of Self-Enhancement Impact of Auto-DebugTo evaluate the impact of auto-debug as described in Section 3.2.3, the performance of AutoBench without debugging is compared with the original version with debugging of AutoBench as shown in Fig. 6(a).",
    "The color segments of a bar in Fig. 6(a) represent the percentage of tasks that finally passed Eval2/Eval1/Eval0 or failed at Eval0.",
